<Body><Title>世界杯险遇恐怖袭击 警方发现犯罪组织欲炸桥</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2014年04月10日</ReportTime>
	<Content><Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e1" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s1">巴西当地媒体</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">4月8日</Time><Denoter did="1" type="statement">报道</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e2" type="thoughtevent"><Object sid="s2">巴西联邦监狱系统</Object><Time tid="t2" type="relTime">日前</Time><Denoter did="d2" type="perception">发现</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e3">一起<Participant sid="s3,s4">犯罪分子</Participant>企图<Denoter did="d3" type="action">炸毁</Denoter>通往世界杯举办城市库里蒂巴的一座<Object oid="o3">桥梁</Object></Event>
以<Event eid="e4"><Denoter did="d4" type="stateChange">破坏</Denoter><Object oid="o4">世界杯</Object></Event>的阴谋。
</Sentence></Paragraph>
　　<Paragraph><Sentence><Event eid="e5" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d5" type="statement">报道</Denoter>说</Event>，
<Event eid="e6"><Object sid="s6,s7,s10">巴西联邦监狱系统</Object><Time tid="t6" type="relTime">去年9月</Time>对<Participant oid="o6">犯罪集团“首都第一司令部”服刑人员</Participant>对话进行了<Denoter did="d6" type="action">监听</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e7" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d7" type="perception">发现</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e8"><Participant sid="s8,s9">两名犯人</Participant>在<Denoter did="d8" type="statement">讨论</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e9"><Denoter did="d9" type="action">炸毁</Denoter>连接库里<Location lid="l9">蒂巴和圣保罗两座城市间116号国道上</Location><Object oid="o9">一座桥梁</Object></Event>的计划，
<Event eid="e10">并将监听<Object oid="o10">内容</Object><Denoter did="d10" type="statement">汇报</Denoter>给了<Participant oid="o10">巴西司法部</Participant></Event>，
<Event eid="e11"><Participant sid="s11">司法部</Participant>立即<Denoter did="d11" type="statement">通知</Denoter><Location lid="l11">库里蒂巴所在的帕拉纳州</Location><Participant oid="o11">公共安全和司法局</Participant>。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
		<Paragraph><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e12" type="thoughtevent"><Object sid="s12">巴西联邦监狱系统</Object>再次<Denoter did="d12" type="statement">强调</Denoter></Event>，
<Event eid="e13">任何在<Location lid="l13">监狱中</Location>的<Object oid="o13">非正常行为</Object>都在<Participant sid="s13">他们</Participant>的<Denoter did="d13" type="action">监控</Denoter>之中</Event>，
<Event eid="e14"><Participant sid="s14,s15">帕拉纳州警方</Participant>也<Denoter did="d14" type="stateChange">做好</Denoter>了各种<Object oid="o14">准备</Object></Event>
				<Event eid="e15" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter did="d15" type="statement">保证</Denoter></Event>
				<Event eid="e16"><Object oid="o16">世界杯</Object>在<Location lid="l16">库里蒂巴</Location>顺利<Denoter did="d16" type="operation">举行</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph></Content>
